      "text": "tick:\nprev-progress-direction = progress-direction\n\nlooking at interaction entity?\n  ✅ progress-direction = +1\n  ❌ progress-direction = -1\n\nprogress += progress-direction\nprogress >= 0\nprogress <= progress-fade-duration\n\nprogress = progress-fade-duration: /return run tag add hold_full\nprogress = 0: /return run tag add hold_none\nprogress-direction > prev-progress-direction: /tag add increasing\nprogress-direction < prev-progress-direction: /tag add decreasing",
